My duty is to guide spirits

5
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,040
to the afterlife.

6
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,960
The afterlife?

7
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,240
You’re

8
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:29,080
a Grim Reaper?

9
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,080
You’re not dreaming.

10
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,680
Stop.

11
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,640
How can a spirit even feel pain?

12
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:56,160
No. I’m not dead.

13
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,680
- You’re dead.
- I’m not.

14
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,640
I’m not dead.

15
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,400
- You’re dead.
- No.

16
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,520
I’m not dead.

17
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,520
Someone! Anyone!

18
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,880
- Help!
- Stop!

19
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,039
Sit down.

20
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,480
You just died,

21
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:29,200
