22
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:34,560
Here’s the thing, there’s a simple way
to prove you’re really dead.

23
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,960
How?

24
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,680
You just…

25
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,640
willingly accept it.

26
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,440
And say

27
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:46,120
"I’m ready."

28
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,240
Go on, try it.

29
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,600
"I’m ready."

30
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,840
I'm rea…

31
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:01,520
