32
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,120
Then you’ll be trapped in this realm.

33
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:11,160
And be what people call

34
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,400
a wandering spirit.

35
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:17,240
So if I don’t say it,

36
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,320
