43
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,040
No.

44
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,960
Maybe I can go back.

45
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:41,280
If I don’t say it,

46
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:44,600
