49
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:50,640
"You only shed tears
when death comes to you."

50
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:53,840
This is the realm beyond time.

51
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:57,160
When one’s time runs out,
they must come here.

52
00:03:57,240 --> 00:04:00,840
That means your time…

53
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,440
