00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:05,120
Accept it.

527
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,080
No.

528
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:08,840
I won’t accept it.

529
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:11,240
I have to go back.

530
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:14,040
I will become a musician.

531
00:42:14,120 --> 00:42:15,600
I will become a doctor.

532
00:42:15,680 --> 00:42:17,760
I’m not ready to leave yet!

533
00:42:25,360 --> 00:42:26,680
<i>From now on,</i>

534
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:28,520
<i>I won't let anyone take away my hope,</i>

535
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:32,400
<i>my dreams, or the life I want to live</i>

536
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,040
ever again.

537
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:36,440
<i>When you refuse to let Alice go,</i>

538
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:40,120
<i>look what happens to your body</i>
<i>in the living world.</i>

539
00:42:42,240 --> 00:42:43,840
Hey! What are you doing?

540
00:42:43,920 --> 00:42:45,360
Get out!

541
00:42:45,440 --> 00:42:47,400
Your time has already ended.

542
00:42:49,160 --> 00:42:51,600
<i>For Alice to keep living,</i>

543
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:52,600
<i>a life must be exchanged.</i>

544
